OL,3,CCritical incidents declared at
OL,4,Chospitals in Midlands over A&E
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FCritical incidents have been declared
OL,8,Fby two NHS trusts in the Midlands amid
OL,9,Fpressure to emergency departments.
OL,11,FSouth Warwickshire University NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust said the level of
OL,13,Fattendances at Warwick Hospital's
OL,14,Faccident and emergency was among the
OL,15,Fhighest it had ever seen.
OL,17,FThe trust says the current situation
OL,18,Fmeans it is unable to maintain the
OL,19,Fwaiting time it "strives for."
