OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FIt says that those seeking care would
OL,8,Fbe waiting a "significant length of
OL,9,Ftime" and asked anyone attending the
OL,10,Fhospital to minimise the number of
OL,11,Fpeople with them.
OL,13,FIn a statement the South Warwickshire
OL,14,FUniversity trust said: "Attendances at
OL,15,FWarwick Hospital's Emergency
OL,16,FDepartment are some of the highest we
OL,17,Fhave ever experienced, and this is
OL,18,Fsignificantly impacting on the time
OL,19,Fpatients are waiting to be seen.
