OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"Clinical teams are trying to see
OL,8,Fpeople as quickly as possible but
OL,9,Fgiven the increased demand we are
OL,10,Funable to maintain the waiting times
OL,11,Fwe usually strive for, therefore
OL,12,Fplease be aware that you may be
OL,13,Fwaiting for a significant length of
OL,14,Ftime and where possible please come
OL,15,Fprepared for this."
OL,17,FA second trust which manages hospital
OL,18,Facross Stoke and Stafford has also
OL,19,Fdeclared a critical incident due to
OL,20,F"extremely high demand" for it's
OL,21,Fservices.
