OL,4,Chospitals in Midlands over A&E
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FThis includes the emergency department
OL,8,Fat Royal Stoke University Hospital and
OL,9,Fthe County Hospital in Stafford.
OL,11,FUniversity Hospitals of North Midlands
OL,12,FTrust last declared a critical
OL,13,Fincident in December.
OL,15,FThe trust Royal Stoke University
OL,16,FHospital is facing ongoing challenges
OL,17,Fas patients were unable to be admitted
OL,18,Fto beds properly and that some
OL,19,Fpatients may face long delays before
OL,20,Fthey are treated.
