OL,7,FBoth trusts say anyone feeling unwell
OL,8,Fis advised not to visit relatives in
OL,9,Fhospital or anyone who is vulnerable
OL,10,Fin the community.
OL,12,FWhen a trust declares a critical
OL,13,Fincident, it means they must take
OL,14,Fadditional steps to maintain safe
OL,15,Fservices for patients and to help cope
OL,16,Fwith the growing pressures.
