OL,7,FMike Goodwin, Deputy Chief Operating
OL,8,FOfficer at University Hospitals of
OL,9,FNorth Midlands Trust, said: "We are
OL,10,Fcurrently experiencing increased
OL,11,Fdemand on our services and are under
OL,12,Fextreme pressure.
OL,14,F"We have therefore taken the decision
OL,15,Fto declare a critical incident. This
OL,16,Fhelps us to take additional measures
OL,17,Fto maintain safe services for our
OL,18,Fpatients.
