OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"Our teams work tirelessly to keep
OL,8,Fpatients safe. We are working with our
OL,9,FNHS and Local Authority partners to
OL,10,Fput in place measures to ensure that
OL,11,Fpeople who need hospital and emergency
OL,12,Fcare can get treatment quickly and to
OL,13,Fidentify and utilise any additional
OL,14,Fcapacity to allow us to discharge
OL,15,Fpatients that do not require hospital
OL,16,Fcare."
